PREFIX orkgp: <http://orkg.org/orkg/predicate/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?model ?modelLabel ?scoreValue WHERE {
  ?contribution orkgp:P32 <http://orkg.org/orkg/resource/R124884> ; orkgp:HAS_BENCHMARK ?benchmark .
  ?benchmark orkgp:HAS_EVALUATION ?evaluation .
  ?evaluation orkgp:HAS_VALUE ?scoreString ; orkgp:HAS_METRIC <http://orkg.org/orkg/resource/R119875> .
  BIND( xsd:decimal ( REPLACE( ?scoreString , " " , "" ) ) AS ?scoreValue ) ?contribution orkgp:HAS_MODEL ?model .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?model rdfs:label ?modelLabel
  }
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?scoreValue )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX orkgp: <http://orkg.org/orkg/predicate/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?metric ?metricLabel ( COUNT( ?bench ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?bench orkgp:HAS_DATASET <http://orkg.org/orkg/resource/R118775> .
  ?bench orkgp:HAS_EVALUATION ?eval .
  ?eval orkgp:HAS_METRIC ?metric .
  ?metric rdfs:label ?metricLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?metricLabel ) = '' || LANGMATCHES( LANG( ?metricLabel ) , 'en' ) )
}
GROUP BY ?metric ?metricLabel
ORDER BY DESC ( ?count )

PREFIX orkgp: <http://orkg.org/orkg/predicate/>
SELECT ?model ?score WHERE {
  ?c orkgp:P32 <http://orkg.org/orkg/resource/R124999> .
  ?c orkgp:P82004 ?score .
  ?c orkgp:HAS_MODEL ?model .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?score )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX orkgc: <http://orkg.org/orkg/class/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX orkgp: <http://orkg.org/orkg/predicate/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?benchmark ?label ?evaluation ?value WHERE {
  ?benchmark rdf:type orkgc:Benchmark .
  ?benchmark orkgp:HAS_DATASET <http://orkg.org/orkg/resource/R121068> .
  ?benchmark rdfs:label ?label .
  ?benchmark orkgp:HAS_EVALUATION ?evaluation .
  ?evaluation orkgp:HAS_VALUE ?value .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( xsd:decimal ( ?value ) )
LIMIT 1

}
